# Project Structure Rules

## Directory Structure
### src (Required)
- analysis/
- utils/
- data/
- prompts/

### results (Required)
- Git ignored
- Contains analysis outputs

### docs (Required)
- Contains project documentation

## Required Files
- README.md
- requirements.txt
- .env_sample
- app.py

## Git Ignored Files
- .env
- *.pyc
- __pycache__
- .DS_Store
- tmp/*

## Dependencies
### Python Version
- Minimum: 3.8

### Required Packages
- streamlit
- pandas
- numpy
- matplotlib
- seaborn
- boto3
- python-dotenv

## Documentation
### Required Files
- README.md
- docs/references.bib

### Format
- Markdown
